    "wd_faq_rrzW4M": {
      "type": "wd-faq",
      "blocks": {
        "item_DrRbLe": {
          "type": "item",
          "settings": {
            "title": "How come you don’t carry XLT (big and tall) sizes?",
            "content": "<p>We know that you’ve seen both regular and longer length t-shirts before, offered in XL (big) and XLT (big and tall) sizing. Now, that’s a lot of options.</p><p>We wanted to simplify the buying experience so we decided to take a fresh approach, by condensing the options to Regular and Longer Length.</p><p>Our Regular Length is often preferred by guys under 6’2”, and boasts a classic traditional cut. If you don’t like your tees too long and are used to buying XL (big) sizes, we recommend this length.</p><p>Our Signature Longer Length suits both big and tall men, with a deeper curved hem. If you are used to buying XLT (big and tall) we recommend this length. But even if you aren’t traditionally buying XLT sizes, but you are looking for extra length for added coverage over your belly and backside, we also recommend this length.</p>"
          }
        },
        "item_MxLErp": {
          "type": "item",
          "settings": {
            "title": "How do I determine my correct size?",
            "content": "<p>Refer to our length and size guide above, where we've got all the measurements laid out for you. Still unsure? Shoot us a message in the chat or fill out the <a href=\"/pages/contact\" title=\"Contact\"><strong>Contact Us</strong></a> form with your measurements, and we'll give you a hand in finding the perfect fit.</p>"
          }
        },
        "item_6VheQ8": {
          "type": "item",
          "settings": {
            "title": "What should I do if I’m in between sizes?",
            "content": "<p>If you're stuck between sizes, we suggest sizing up for a bit more breathing room. It's a smart move - gives you some wiggle room, and if your gear shrinks slightly in the wash, you're still covered.</p>"
          }
        },
        "item_GxhcTd": {
          "type": "item",
          "settings": {
            "title": "Will the clothing shrink after washing?",
            "content": "<p>Our fabric isn't pre-shrunk, so you can realistically expect a 3-5% shrinkage at most. To keep it to a minimum, we recommend washing in cold water and hang drying or using the lowest heat setting possible.</p>"
          }
        },
        "item_fHBzy6": {
          "type": "item",
          "settings": {
            "title": "What is your return policy for items that don’t fit?",
            "content": "<p>We want you to love your Strongsize gear. If you are having second thoughts, we are happy to offer returns within 30 days after delivery.</p><p><strong>Returns</strong></p><p>We offer free returns for store credit. All cash refunds are subject to an $8 return fee. Items must be unworn, unwashed, and in their original packaging.</p><p><a href=\"https://strongsize.loopreturns.com/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://strongsize.loopreturns.com\"><strong>Start a return</strong></a></p>"
          }
        },
        "item_jqydgJ": {
          "type": "item",
          "settings": {
            "title": "Can I get personalized fit advice before making a purchase?",
            "content": "<p>Of course! <a href=\"/pages/contact\" title=\"Contact\"><strong>Contact Us</strong></a> or hit us up in the chat and we will respond as fast as we can, usually within 24 hours!</p>"
          }
        },
        "item_LgHKFN": {
          "type": "item",
          "settings": {
            "title": "Does the fabric stretch out throughout daily wear?",
            "content": "<p>Our Everyday Collection is made from our Bounceback™ Stretch Cotton Jersey, which is crafted from a blend of 95% cotton and 5% spandex. </p><p>Here's the deal: cotton is cool because it's soft and breathes well, but it has a habit of stretching out a bit when you wear it. That's where the spandex comes into play - that 5% gives the fabric some stretchiness that snaps back into shape. This means our tops can keep up with you all day, every day.</p>"
          }
        }
      },
